    "data": [
        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結　油價全星期狂升35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"659\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V80IwHgCOc2XuFxBxcc4tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b773aef0-19ab-11f1-b3b3-efcef343179f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日，星期五。關鍵的每月就業報告意外轉弱，市場對通脹的憂慮升溫，三大指數皆下跌。美股經歷動盪一周後，好消息是美股明天喘定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指下跌0.9%，即逾450點，是跌幅最少的指數；以科技股為主的納指數下跌約1.6%；標普500指數下跌1.3%。三大指數全周均錄得跌幅，標普500指數累跌2%，道指更挫3%，納指則跌約1%。而由年初至今亦已轉為下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因霍爾木茲海峽油輪運輸幾乎陷入停滯，市場擔心波斯灣出口國在儲存空間耗盡後可能被迫減產。同時，美國與以色列對伊朗的戰事仍未見緩和跡象，特朗普今天表示，解決衝突的唯一途徑是「無條件投降」。油價升至逾90元，全星期累計升幅高達35%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f4baba21-8022-4470-a2fa-a4e0070d16ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日（星期五）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌453.19點或0.95%，報47,501.55點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌90.69點或1.33%，報6,740.02點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌361.31點或1.59%，報22,387.68點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報91.27美元一桶，升10.26美元或12.67%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,181.3美元一盎司，升102.6美元或2.02%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報68,119.67美元，跌3,128.45美元或4.39%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.133厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月就業報告顯示，非農就業職位意外減少92,000個，遠遜於市場預期的新增55,000個；失業率亦上升至4.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勞動市場轉弱，加上中東衝突推高油價，令市場憂慮出現滯脹，亦即經濟增長疲弱與通脹上升同時出現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價狂升，航空股最為受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國航空;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAL/\">美國航空</a>(AAL.US)挫5.2%，美聯航(UAL.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:達美航空;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/DAL/\">達美航空</a>(DAL.US)均跌逾3%。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Caterpillar;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CAT/\">Caterpillar</a>(CAT.US)跌3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大型科技股走弱，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">英偉達</a>(NVDA.US)挫3%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>(META.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>(AMZN.US)、特斯拉(TSLA.US)均跌逾2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:蘋果;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL/\">蘋果</a>(AAPL.US)、Alphabet(GOOG.US)跌約1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特普在周五呼籲伊朗「無條件投降」，亦會晤多家美國主要國防承包商高層，包括<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:16;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Lockheed Martin;cpos:16;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/LMT/\">Lockheed Martin</a>(LMT.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:17;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:波音;cpos:17;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BA/\">波音</a>(BA.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:18;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:RTX;cpos:18;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/RTX/\">RTX</a>(RTX.US)及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:19;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Northrop Grumman;cpos:19;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOC/\">Northrop Grumman</a>(NOC.US)等軍工商。相關軍工股普遍升約2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外界憂慮隨著對伊朗戰事持續接近一周且未見結束跡象，美軍武器庫存正逐步消耗，白宮則淡化武器庫存下降的憂慮，強調美軍軍火庫存充足。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C-%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%B5%82%E7%B5%90-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%85%A8%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E7%8B%82%E5%8D%8735-223632886.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 06:43:38",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "甲骨文股價因德州數據中心計劃取消報導而下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/64M9sATm19uqdzdtp4hFYw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7B05U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 甲骨文公司(NYSE:ORCL)股價在週五最後一個交易小時下跌1%,此前彭博社報導該公司與OpenAI終止了擴建德州數據中心的計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該股在消息傳出前曾一度上漲3%。在抹去漲幅並下跌1%後,股價隨後企穩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>甲骨文</span></span>與OpenAI取消了擴建德州阿比林市旗艦人工智能數據中心的計劃,原因是融資談判拖延以及OpenAI需求的變化,據彭博社報導。談判破裂為Meta Platforms Inc.(NASDAQ:META)創造了機會,該公司正考慮從開發商Crusoe租賃計劃中的擴建場地。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eb5afc38-2836-3047-9902-07dca1869333-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社報導,人工智能芯片製造商英偉達(NASDAQ:NVDA)協助促成了Meta與開發商的討論。英偉達向Crusoe支付了1.5億美元按金,並開始協助爭取Meta成為擴建項目的租戶。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Crusoe在阿比林開發的1,000英畝園區是Stargate項目的一部分,該項目曾在白宮與總統唐納德·特朗普一同宣布。雖然該場地的多個部分已經投入運營,但甲骨文和OpenAI決定不繼續推進租賃大規模擴建的初步計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">甲骨文和OpenAI在Stargate場地使用英偉達的人工智能半導體。隨著Crusoe尋找租戶,英偉達參與其中以確保其產品仍將填充擴建的數據中心,而不是競爭對手Advanced Micro Devices Inc.(NASDAQ:AMD)的產品。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B2%E9%AA%A8%E6%96%87%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%A0%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%9E%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-212325586.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 06:17:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "甲骨文和OpenAI終止擴建旗艦數據中心的計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:甲骨文;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/甲骨文\">甲骨文</a>和OpenAI已取消在德克薩斯州擴建一座旗艦人工智能(AI)<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:數據中心;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/數據中心\">數據中心</a>的計畫，此前磋商因融資問題和OpenAI不斷變化的需求而久拖不決。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，談判破裂為Meta Platforms Inc.介入創造了機會，Meta考慮從開發商Crusoe手中租賃位於德州阿比林的擬擴建場地。因談判非公開而不願具名的知情人士稱，人工智能晶片製造商輝達協助促成Meta與這家開發商之間的洽談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">計畫的變動凸顯建設AI數據中心的複雜性。這類項目預計耗資數百億美元，且需要眾多合作夥伴協同推進。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dfb448c4-f20a-3f2f-8f01-f5b4c958a1bb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Crusoe在阿比林開發的園區屬於備受關注的Stargate項目的一部分。該項目去年由總統唐納德·川普在白宮宣布。知情人士稱，儘管占地1,000英畝的園區仍在建設中，且部分設施已投入運營，但甲骨文和OpenAI已決定不再推進租賃大規模擴建部分的暫定計畫。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">甲骨文與OpenAI在該園區使用輝達的AI半導體。知情人士稱，由於Crusoe正在尋找租戶，輝達已介入以確保擴建後的數據中心繼續採用其產品，而非競爭對手AMD的晶片。知情人士稱，輝達已向Crusoe支付1.5億美元保證金，並開始協助爭取Meta成為擴建項目的租戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">甲骨文去年7月同意為OpenAI開發4.5吉瓦的數據中心容量。該協議仍在推進中，雙方還宣布了其他地點的多個項目，例如位於底特律附近、由Related Digital擁有的項目。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，自2025年年中以來，甲骨文、Crusoe和OpenAI一直在討論將阿比林數據中心容量從1.2吉瓦擴至約2.0吉瓦。1吉瓦相當於一座核反應堆的發電能力，可在同一時點為約75萬戶家庭供電。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，談判曠日持久，且因融資問題及OpenAI需求預測頻繁變化而更加複雜，最終破裂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，甲骨文和Crusoe之間的關係還因園區的可靠性問題而承壓。知情人士稱，今年早些時候，因冬季天氣影響部分液冷設備，數據中心建築曾停運數日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩家公司均表示雙方關係依然穩固，阿比林園區的甲骨文租賃項目進展迅速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Meta與OpenAI拒絕置評。輝達未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，Meta與Crusoe圍繞阿比林擴建項目的談判仍在進行中，且可能存在變數。Meta目前正在路易斯安那州和印第安納州建設多個大型數據中心。上月，Meta達成協議，將部署規模6吉瓦的AMD設備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Oracle and OpenAI End Plans to Expand Flagship Data Center</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Shirin Ghaffary、Ian King、Kurt Wagner.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B2%E9%AA%A8%E6%96%87%E5%92%8Copenai%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E6%93%B4%E5%BB%BA%E6%97%97%E8%89%A6%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-211113845.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 05:47:34",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "長和旗下公司對巴拿馬政府啟動國際仲裁 索賠至少20億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 長江和記實業有限公司旗下巴拿馬港口公司已就巴拿馬政府「非法接管」巴爾博亞港和<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:克里斯托瓦爾港;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/克里斯托瓦爾港\">克里斯托瓦爾港</a>兩個貨櫃碼頭一事，對該國政府啟動國際仲裁，索償至少20億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周五發布的聲明，巴拿馬港口公司已根據國際商會仲裁規則啟動國際仲裁。該公司稱巴拿馬政府在新聞言論中對索償金額做出失實陳述。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司就巴拿馬政府2月23日的行政法令提出法律追索權。該法令命令強行接管公司所有資產及專有且受法律保護的文件及資料。該公司還要求即時取回及歸還相關文件及資料。長和也根據雙邊投資條約就其早前發出的爭議通知提交補充資料，指出巴拿馬政府拒絕進一步磋商，在欠缺透明度的情況下實施強行接管。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-178df13b-e052-3480-9d7f-eaadbeb8c0ee-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聲明表示，巴拿馬港口公司與長和寸步不讓，將就巴拿馬政府嚴重違約及反投資者行為，全數追索其應得的一切權益。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上個月，巴拿馬在川普施壓下接管長和運營的兩座港口。長和於去年3月宣布將上述兩個港口及其他41個港口出售給貝萊德牽頭的財團。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：巴拿馬接管長和運營的兩座港口 港府提出嚴正抗議</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這筆預計將使長和一年前獲得逾190億美元現金的交易在過去一年來進展甚微。據彭博新聞此前報導，目前各方把希望寄托在川普與習近平即將進行的會晤取得政治突破之上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：長和港口交易遲遲不見下文 川普與習近平的峰會成為希望所在</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題CK Hutchison Unit Seeks $2 Billion in Panama Ports Dispute</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E5%92%8C%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%8D%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81-%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9120%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-195532039.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 04:32:34",
